high_descs: Turn right, walk a few steps toward, turn right, walk passed the coffee table, turn right to the middle of the table, and then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the left remote from the table.
Turn right to the edge of the table, turn left and walk towards the gray sofa chair.
Place the remote on the middle of the chair.
Turn left and walk towards the blue sofa on your right.
Pick up the remote on the sofa.
Turn right and head towards the gray sofa chair on your left.
Place the remote to the left of the remote on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place two tv remotes on the gray sofa chair.

high_descs: Move to the coffee table in front of the checkered couch
Pick up the remote control from the coffee table
Move to the grey arm chair to the right of the blue couch
Place remote on to the arm chair
Move to the blue couch to the left of the grey arm chair
Pick up remote control from off the couch
Move to the grey arm chair to the right of the blue couch
Place remote next to the other one on the arm chair
anns.task_desc: Put two remote controls on to the grey arm chair

high_descs: Turn right and walk two steps then turn right and walk over to the couch and then turn right and walk so you are facing the middle of the coffee table looking at the wall with the blue couch.
Pick up the remote more towards the center of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk a few steps then turn left and walk so you are facing the brown chair to the right of the blue couch.
Place the remote on the chairs cushion.
Now turn around and walk over to the blue couch so you are facing the right side of it.
Pick up the remote on the right side of the blue couch.
Walk back over to the brown chair.
Place the remote to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on a brown chair.
